Gissa to pay dividend 0 . 8315 pesos / shr . Mexican industrial company Grupo Industrial Saltillo ( Gissa ) said Wednesday that from May 9 it will pay a dividend of 0 . 8315 pesos per share to holders of coupon 29 . The dividend payment was agreed by shareholders at the company ' s annual meeting , Giussa said in a statement to the Mexican Stock Exchange . ( ( - - Chris Aspin , Mexico City newsroom + 525 7289530 ) ) 
